00:00:11.710 --> 00:00:13.260
&gt;&gt; Really, what does it say?

00:00:13.260 --> 00:00:15.850
&gt;&gt; Some pretty cool stuff here. Actually, I've got

00:00:15.850 --> 00:00:20.330
blue eyes, apparently. my blood type is O positive.

00:00:20.330 --> 00:00:22.900
I seem to be able to digest lactose products

00:00:22.900 --> 00:00:26.950
pretty well. I can't taste bitter flavors. A cup

00:00:26.950 --> 00:00:28.420
of coffee late at night doesn't bother

00:00:28.420 --> 00:00:31.250
me, because I metabolize caffeine pretty quickly,

00:00:31.250 --> 00:00:35.640
