00:00:54.920 --> 00:00:58.380
your genome is. A unique sequence of letters that has the

00:00:58.380 --> 00:01:01.060
information to make up who you are. So, you're saying,

00:01:01.060 --> 00:01:03.560
all of the cells in my body, they're just little letters?

00:01:03.560 --> 00:01:07.010
&gt;&gt; Well, I guess so, in a sense. your genome's a

